						               													<description>War, Battle of Two Kingdoms is a team vs team card game. Use your army of knights, archers and wizards to destroy the other team's castle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Both teams will have 3 team members,each controlling a different army type, each with their own card deck. Any deck not controlled by a human player, will have their top card played each turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player starts with their deck of cards, shuffle and draw 3 cards. Each turn, all players will play one card from their hand, or top card of a deck not controlled by a player. You can tell your team what you are planning to do, but then the other team will hear you, you may not show your hand to your team.&amp;#10;The cards will be flipped up at the same time and played out in alphabetical order. Generally, the wizard will play first, casting a spell on the battle field, followed by the archers to kill as many knights as possible, then the team that has the most knights left over after the wizard's and the archer's onslaught will destroy an enemy's wall.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each deck has their ultra actions, wizards have a fireball to annihilate all cards played this turn and remove them from the game and destroy a wall from both team's castle.&amp;#10;Archers can kill a enemy's wizard before they cast their spell.&amp;#10;Knight have a Juggernaut which is very hard to defeat and almost every time destroy the enemy's castle wall.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All cards in each player's deck will be used, once a player plays a card they will redraw at the end of the turn, but once the draw pile is used up, players will use the remaining cards in their hand before reshuffling their cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal of the game is to destroy the other teams castle, first team to destroy the other team's castle wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
